org.mitre.provenance.plusobject

Class PLUSInvocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mitre.provenance.surrogate.Surrogateable
      • org.mitre.provenance.plusobject.PLUSObject
        • org.mitre.provenance.plusobject.PLUSInvocation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Comparable<Object>, SourcedObject, PropertyCapable

    public class PLUSInvocation
extends PLUSObject
    Models an invocation as a type of PLUS node. Invocations depend on activities and workflows. Note that this object initially stores only the ID suitable for fetching those objects. It does not automatically load those objects. Because they are mutually dependent, you have to be careful not to have automatic code that causes one to load the other recursively.
    Author:
    DMALLEN
